msgstr ""
"A úsáidtear i leagan-rialú gealltanas. Fanann an seoladh sa stór go deo "
"nuair a bhíonn athruithe geallta ag Weblate."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:219 weblate/accounts/models.py:978
msgid "Commit name"
msgstr "Ainm tiomantais"

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:222
msgid ""
"Used in version control commits. The name stays in the repository forever, "
"once changes are committed by Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear é i ngealltanais rialaithe leaganacha. Fanann an t-ainm sa "
"stórlann go deo, a luaithe a dhéanann Weblate athruithe."

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:250
msgid "Use anonymous account name"
msgstr "Úsáid ainm cuntais gan ainm"

