msgstr "Ríomhphost cuntais"

#: weblate/accounts/forms.py:419
msgid ""
"Used for e-mail notifications and as a commit e-mail if it is not configured "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear é le haghaidh fógraí ríomhphoist agus mar r-phost geallta mura "
"bhfuil sé cumraithe thíos."

