"Tá an stór as dáta, seans nach bhfaighidh tú torthaí ionchais go dtí go "
"ndéanann tú é a nuashonrú."

#: weblate/addons/cdn.py:155
msgid "JavaScript localization CDN"
msgstr "Logánú JavaScript CDN"

#: weblate/addons/cdn.py:157
msgid ""
"Publishes translations into content delivery network for use in JavaScript "
"or HTML localization."
msgstr ""
"Foilsíonn sé aistriúcháin go líonra seachadta inneachair le húsáid i logánú "
"JavaScript nó HTML."

#: weblate/addons/cdn.py:269
msgid "Translation files CDN"
msgstr "Comhaid aistriúcháin CDN"

#: weblate/addons/cdn.py:271
msgid "Publishes translation files into a content delivery network."
msgstr "Foilsíonn sé comhaid aistriúcháin i líonra seachadta ábhair."

#: weblate/addons/cdn.py:308
msgid "The translation files CDN add-on cannot publish weblate.js."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir leis an mbreiseán CDN comhaid aistriúcháin weblate.js a fhoilsiú."

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:44
msgid "Cleanup translation files"
msgstr "Glanadh comhaid aistriúcháin"

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:46
msgid ""
"Update all translation files to match the monolingual base file. For most "
"file formats, this means removing stale translation keys no longer present "
"in the base file."
msgstr ""
"Nuashonraigh gach comhad aistriúcháin chun teacht leis an mbunchomhad "
"aonteangach. Don chuid is mó de na formáidí comhaid, ciallaíonn sé seo go "
"mbaintear seaneochracha aistriúcháin nach bhfuil sa bhunchomhad a thuilleadh."

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:93
msgid "Remove blank strings"
msgstr "Bain teaghráin bhána"

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:95
msgid "Removes strings without a translation from translation files."
msgstr "Bain teaghráin gan aistriú ó chomhaid aistriúcháin."

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:130
msgid "Reset repository to upstream"
msgstr "Athshocraigh an stór go dtí an sruth"

#: weblate/addons/cleanup.py:132
msgid "Discards all changes in the Weblate repository each night."
msgstr "Caitheann sé gach athrú sa stór Weblate gach oíche."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:91
msgid "Add missing languages"
msgstr "Cuir teangacha atá in easnamh leis"

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:93
msgid ""
"Ensures a consistent set of languages is used for all components within a "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Cinntíonn sé go mbaintear úsáid as tacar comhsheasmhach teangacha do gach "
"comhpháirt de thionscadal."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:129
msgid ""
"This add-on affects the whole project and may create translation files "
"across many components or repositories."
msgstr ""
"Bíonn tionchar ag an mbreiseán seo ar an tionscadal ar fad agus féadfaidh sé "
"comhaid aistriúcháin a chruthú i go leor comhpháirteanna nó stórtha."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:134
msgid ""
"This add-on affects the whole category and may create translation files "
"across many components or repositories."
msgstr ""
"Bíonn tionchar ag an mbreiseán seo ar an gcatagóir ar fad agus féadfaidh sé "
"comhaid aistriúcháin a chruthú thar go leor comhpháirteanna nó stórtha."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:138
msgid ""
"This add-on affects all projects and may create translation files across "
"many components or repositories."
msgstr ""
"Bíonn tionchar ag an mbreiseán seo ar gach tionscadal agus féadfaidh sé "
"comhaid aistriúcháin a chruthú i go leor comhpháirteanna nó stórtha."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:244 weblate/trans/models/component.py:5279
msgid ""
"The given language maps to a different language. Check language aliases "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Mapálann an teanga tugtha chuig teanga eile. Seiceáil socruithe "
"leasainmneacha teanga."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:248 weblate/trans/models/component.py:5285
msgid "The given language is used as a source language."
msgstr "Úsáidtear an teanga tugtha mar theanga fhoinseach."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:253 weblate/trans/models/component.py:5297
msgid "The language filter timed out."
msgstr "Chuaigh an scagaire teanga in éag."

#: weblate/addons/consistency.py:256 weblate/trans/models/component.py:5301
msgid "The given language is filtered by the language filter."
msgstr "Tá an teanga tugtha scagtha ag an scagaire teanga."

#: weblate/addons/discovery.py:27
msgid "Component discovery"
msgstr "Fionnachtain Comhpháirte"

#: weblate/addons/discovery.py:29
msgid ""
"Automatically adds or removes project components based on file changes in "
"the version control system."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann nó baintear comhpháirteanna tionscadail go huathoibríoch bunaithe "
"ar athruithe comhaid sa chóras rialaithe leagain."

#: weblate/addons/example.py:31
msgid "Example add-on"
msgstr "Sampla de bhreiseán"

#: weblate/addons/example.py:33
msgid "This add-on does nothing it is just an example."
msgstr "Ní dhéanann an breiseán seo rud ar bith. Níl ach sampla atá ann."

#: weblate/addons/example_pre.py:25
msgid "Execute script before commit"
msgstr "Rith an script roimh chimiú"

#: weblate/addons/example_pre.py:26
msgid "This add-on executes a script."
msgstr "Feidhmíonn an breiseán seo script."

#: weblate/addons/fedora_messaging.py:32
msgid "Fedora Messaging"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí Fedora"

#: weblate/addons/fedora_messaging.py:34
msgid "Sends notifications to a Fedora Messaging compatible AMQP exchange."
msgstr ""
"Seolann sé fógraí chuig malartán AMQP atá comhoiriúnach le Fedora Messaging."

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:51
msgid "Flag new source strings as \"Needs checking\""
msgstr "Brataigh teaghráin foinse nua mar \"Riachtanas seiceála\""

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:53
msgid ""
"Whenever a new source string is imported from the VCS, it is flagged as "
"needing checking in Weblate. This way you can easily filter and edit source "
"strings written by the developers."
msgstr ""
"Aon uair a iompórtáiltear teaghrán foinse nua ón VCS, cuirtear bratach air "
"mar rud a bhfuil gá le seiceáil air i Weblate. Ar an mbealach seo is féidir "
"leat teaghráin foinse scríofa ag na forbróirí a scagadh agus a chur in eagar "
"go héasca."

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:72
msgid "Flag new translations as \"Needs rewriting\""
msgstr "Brataigh aistriúcháin nua mar \"Riachtanas athscríofa\""

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:74
msgid ""
"Whenever a new translatable string is imported from the VCS, it is flagged "
"as needing rewriting in Weblate. This way you can easily filter and edit "
"translations created by the developers."
msgstr ""
"Aon uair a allmhairítear teaghrán nua inaistrithe ón VCS, cuirtear bratach "
"air mar theaghrán a bhfuil gá é a athscríobh i Weblate. Ar an mbealach seo "
"is féidir leat aistriúcháin a chruthaigh na forbróirí a scagadh agus a chur "
"in eagar go héasca."

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:90
msgid "Flag unchanged translations as \"Needs rewriting\""
msgstr "Brataigh aistriúcháin gan athrú mar \"Riachtanas athscríofa\""

#: weblate/addons/flags.py:92
msgid ""
"Whenever a new translatable string is imported from the VCS and it matches a "
"source string, it is flagged as needing rewriting in Weblate. Especially "
"useful for file formats that include source strings for untranslated strings."
msgstr ""
"Aon uair a allmhairítear teaghrán nua inaistrithe ón VCS agus go bhfuil sé "
"ag teacht le teaghrán foinse, cuirtear bratach air mar theaghrán a bhfuil gá "
"é a athscríobh i Weblate. Tá sé seo an-úsáideach go háirithe i gcás formáidí "
"comhaid ina bhfuil teaghráin foinse do theaghráin neamhaistrithe."

