msgid "Updates gettext headers and replaces placeholder POT comments."
msgstr ""
"Nuashonraíonn sé ceanntásca gettext agus cuireann sé tuairimí POT in ionad "
"na n-áitchoinneálaí."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:159
msgid "Update PO files using msgmerge"
msgstr "Nuashonraigh comhaid PO ag baint úsáide as msgmerge"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:164
msgid ""
"Ensures the msgmerge add-on is installed and triggers it after the POT file "
"is updated."
msgstr ""
"Cinntíonn sé go bhfuil an breiseán msgmerge suiteáilte agus go spreagann sé "
"é tar éis an comhad POT a nuashonrú."

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:189
msgid "Do not extract comments"
msgstr "Ná bain amach tuairimí"

#: weblate/addons/forms.py:190
