"The Meson add-on expects a Meson gettext directory with meson.build and "
"POTFILES or POTFILES.in."
msgstr ""
"Tá an breiseán Meson ag súil le heolaire gettext Meson le meson.build agus "
"POTFILES nó POTFILES.in."

