#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:15
msgid "CSRF verification failed. Request aborted."
msgstr "Theip ar fhíorú CSRF. Cuireadh deireadh leis an iarratas."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:19
msgid ""
"This HTTPS site requires a 'Referer' header to be sent by your web browser, "
"but none was sent. This header is required for security reasons, ensuring "
"that your browser is not being hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Teastaíonn ceanntásc ‘Referer’ ón suíomh HTTPS seo le bheith seolta ag do "
"bhrabhsálaí gréasáin, ach níor seoladh ceann ar bith. Tá an ceanntásc seo ag "
"teastáil ar chúiseanna slándála, ag cinntiú nach bhfuil do bhrabhsálaí á "
"fuadach ag tríú páirtithe."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:22
msgid ""
"If you have set up your web browser to not send 'Referer' headers,  you need "
"to turn that on (at least for this site, HTTPS connections, or 'same-origin' "
"requests)."
msgstr ""
"Má tá do bhrabhsálaí gréasáin socraithe agat chun gan ceanntásca ‘Tagairtí’ "
"a sheoladh, ní mór duit é sin a chur ar siúl (ar a laghad i gcás an tsuímh "
"seo, naisc HTTPS, nó iarratais ‘an tionscnaimh chéanna’)."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:26
msgid ""
"Our site requires a session cookie to make the forms work. This cookie is "
"required for security reasons, ensuring that your browser is not being "
"hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Teastaíonn fianán seisiúin ar ár suíomh chun go n-oibreoidh na foirmeacha. "
"Tá an fianán seo ag teastáil ar chúiseanna slándála, ag cinntiú nach bhfuil "
"do bhrabhsálaí á fuadach ag tríú páirtithe."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:29
msgid ""
"It might have happened that your session cookie expired due to inactivity. "
"This can easily happen for unauthenticated requests where session validity "
"is limited. You might want to try your intended action again in such a case."
msgstr ""
"Seans gur tharla gur chuaigh do fhianán seisiúin in éag mar gheall ar "
"neamhghníomhaíocht. Is féidir leis seo tarlú go héasca d’iarratais "
"neamhfhíordheimhnithe nuair a bhíonn bailíocht seisiúin teoranta. B'fhéidir "
"gur mhaith leat triail a bhaint as an ngníomh atá beartaithe agat arís i "
"gcás dá leithéid."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:32
msgid ""
"If you have set up your browser to not save cookies, you need to enable "
"saving them (at least for this site, or 'same-origin' requests)."
msgstr ""
"Má tá do bhrabhsálaí socraithe agat chun nach sábhálfaidh tú fianáin, ní mór "
"duit iad a shábháil (ar a laghad don suíomh seo, nó iarratais 'ar an mbunús "
"céanna')."

#: weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:36
#, python-format
msgid "CSRF failure reason: %(reason)s"
msgstr "Cúis teipe CSRF: %(reason)s"

