#: weblate/templates/accounts/recovery-codes.html:25
msgid ""
"Recovery codes can be used to access your account if you lose access to your "
"device and cannot receive two-factor authentication codes."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir cóid athshlánaithe a úsáid chun rochtain a fháil ar do chuntas má "
"chailleann tú rochtain ar do ghléas agus mura féidir leat cóid "
"fíordheimhnithe dhá fhachtóir a fháil."

#: weblate/templates/accounts/recovery-codes.html:29
msgid ""
"Keep your recovery codes in a safe spot, like in a password manager. These "
"codes are the last resort for accessing your account in case you lose your "
"password and other second factors. If you cannot find these codes when "
"needed, you will lose access to your account."
msgstr ""
"Coinnigh do chóid athshlánaithe in áit shábháilte, cosúil le bainisteoir "
"pasfhocail. Is iad na cóid seo an rogha dheireanach chun rochtain a fháil ar "
"do chuntas ar eagla go gcaillfidh tú do phasfhocal agus fachtóirí eile dara. "
"Mura féidir leat na cóid seo a aimsiú nuair is gá, caillfidh tú rochtain ar "
"do chuntas."

#: weblate/templates/accounts/recovery-codes.html:40
