msgstr "Is féidir leat teagmháil a dhéanamh linn le haghaidh tuilleadh sonraí."

#: weblate/templates/accounts/removal.html:16
msgid "Account removal"
msgstr "Baint cuntais"

#: weblate/templates/accounts/removal.html:24
msgid ""
"You will lose access to the projects you manage. Projects themselves will "
