#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/ambiguouslanguage.html:4
msgid "Files for translated languages are using ambiguous language codes."
msgstr "Tá cóid teanga débhríoch in úsáid ag comhaid do theangacha aistrithe."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/ambiguouslanguage.html:5
msgid ""
"These language codes indicate a macrolanguage, and it is usually better to "
"use the code of the individual language instead."
msgstr ""
"Léiríonn na cóid teanga seo macratheanga, agus de ghnáth is fearr cód na "
"teanga aonair a úsáid ina ionad."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/ambiguouslanguage.html:14
msgid "Suggested individual language codes"
msgstr "Cóid teanga aonair molta"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/billinglimit.html:4
msgid ""
"Your billing plan has exceeded its limits. You can still use the service, "
"but are recommended to upgrade the billing plan."
msgstr ""
"Tá do phlean billeála sáraithe a theorainneacha. Is féidir leat an tseirbhís "
"a úsáid fós, ach moltar duit an plean billeála a uasghrádú."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not validate the repository browser URL:"
msgstr "Níorbh fhéidir le Weblate URL brabhsálaí an stórais a bhailíochtú:"

#. Translators: This is for the case where the link check fails in Weblate, but the links (shown above this message) work correctly for the user.
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:14
msgid ""
"In case the above links work for you, they might just require "
"authentication, and it is safe to dismiss this alert."
msgstr ""
"Sa chás go n-oibreoidh na naisc thuas duit, seans go mbeidh fíordheimhniú ag "
"teastáil uathu, agus tá sé sábháilte an foláireamh seo a dhíbhe."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenbrowserurl.html:18
msgid ""
"This can happen if the path within the translation files contains references "
"to a parent directory, or is absolute."
msgstr ""
"Féadfaidh sé seo tarlú má tá tagairtí d'eolaire tuismitheora sa chonair "
"laistigh de na comhaid aistriúcháin, nó má tá sé absalóideach."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/brokenprojecturl.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not validate the project website URL:"
msgstr ""
"Níorbh fhéidir le Weblate URL shuíomh gréasáin an tionscadail a bhailíochtú:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/cdnaddonerror.html:3
msgid "Weblate CDN add-on could not parse the HTML files."
msgstr "Níorbh fhéidir an breiseán CDN Weblate na comhaid HTML a pharsáil."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/cdnaddonerror.html:10
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/parseerror.html:10
msgid "Filename"
msgstr "Ainm comhaid"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:5
msgid ""
"The upstream repository was not found. Please check whether it exists and is "
"accessible to Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Níor aimsíodh an stór in aghaidh an tsrutha. Seiceáil an bhfuil sé ann agus "
"an bhfuil rochtain ag Weblate air."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:11
msgid ""
"The upstream repository could not be accessed. Please check whether it is "
"accessible to Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Níorbh fhéidir an stór in aghaidh an tsrutha a rochtain. Seiceáil le do "
"thoil an bhfuil rochtain ag Weblate air."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:17
msgid ""
"Gerrit prohibited this push. You might need a gerrit-account that has the "
"forge author permissions for the repository/branch or have to use the squash "
"add-on on this component in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Chuir Gerrit cosc ar an mbrú seo. B’fhéidir go mbeadh cuntas gerrit ag "
"teastáil uait a bhfuil ceadanna údair forge aige don stór/bhrainse nó go "
"mbeadh ort an breiseán squash a úsáid ar an gcomhpháirt seo i Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:22
msgid ""
"The upstream repository could not be temporarily accessed. Please try it "
"again later."
msgstr ""
"Níorbh fhéidir an stór in aghaidh an tsrutha a rochtain go sealadach. Bain "
"triail eile as ar ball."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:29
msgid ""
"Your repository URL seems to miss credentials. Either provide them in the "
"URL or use SSH with key based authentication."
msgstr ""
"Is cosúil go bhfuil na dintiúir in easnamh ar do URL stórtha. Cuir ar fáil "
"iad san URL nó bain úsáid as SSH le fíordheimhniú eochairbhunaithe."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:35
msgid "You might want to use following URL instead:"
msgstr "Seans gur mhaith leat an URL seo a leanas a úsáid ina ionad sin:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:41
msgid ""
"You might want to choose Git with force push as version control system in "
"the component configuration to overwrite the remote repository after "
"rebasing commits in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"B'fhéidir gur mhaith leat Git le brú fórsa a roghnú mar chóras rialaithe "
"leagain i gcumraíocht an chomhpháirte chun an cian-stór a scríobh tar éis "
"gealltanas a athbhunú in Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:45
msgid ""
"The Weblate repository is missing some commits from upstream. Perhaps it is "
"not receiving notifications upon updates of the remote repository."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt gealltanas in easnamh ar stór Weblate ó in aghaidh an tsrutha. "
"B'fhéidir nach bhfuil sé ag fáil fógraí faoi nuashonruithe ar an gcianstór."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/common-repo.html:50
msgid ""
"Weblate will retry the operation once it is needed again, so the alert might "
"disappear for the temporary issues."
msgstr ""
"Déanfaidh Weblate an oibríocht a thriail arís nuair a bheidh sé ag teastáil "
"arís, agus mar sin seans go n-imeoidh an foláireamh as fadhbanna sealadacha."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:4
msgid ""
"Another component is configured to push to the same repository and push "
"branch."
msgstr ""
"Tá comhpháirt eile cumraithe chun brú chuig an stór céanna agus brainse a "
"bhrú."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:5
msgid "This can cause the branch to be overwritten."
msgstr "D’fhéadfadh sé seo a bheith ina chúis le róscríobh an bhrainse."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/conflictingrepositorysetup.html:9
msgid ""
"Use a different push branch for each component, or share the repository "
"using the following Weblate URL:"
msgstr ""
"Bain úsáid as brainse brú difriúil do gach comhpháirt, nó roinn an stórlann "
"ag baint úsáide as an URL Weblate seo a leanas:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:4
msgid ""
"Some linked components have the same file mask or share some of the files."
msgstr ""
"Tá an masc comhaid céanna ag roinnt comhpháirteanna nasctha nó roinneann "
"siad cuid de na comhaid."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:5
msgid "Please fix this by removing one of them."
msgstr "Déan é seo a shocrú le do thoil trí cheann acu a bhaint."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatefilemask.html:8
msgid "The following files were found multiple times:"
msgstr "Fuarthas na comhaid seo a leanas go minic:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:5
msgid "The component contains translation file for the source language."
msgstr "Tá comhad aistriúcháin don teanga fhoinseach sa chomhpháirt."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:7
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:35
msgid "Please consider the following:"
msgstr "Déan machnamh ar na nithe seo a leanas le do thoil:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:12
msgid ""
"You might be using a monolingual translation file as a bilingual one. If "
"that is the case, please set the monolingual base language file location."
msgstr ""
"Seans go bhfuil comhad aistriúcháin aonteangach á úsáid agat mar chomhad "
"dátheangach. Más é sin an cás, socraigh suíomh an chomhaid bhunteanga "
"aonteangach."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:16
msgid ""
"In case translation to the source language is desired, please change the "
"source language in the component settings."
msgstr ""
"Ar eagla go bhfuil aistriúchán go dtí an teanga foinse ag teastáil, athraigh "
"an teanga foinse sna socruithe comhpháirte."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:19
msgid ""
"If the translation file for the source language is not needed, please remove "
"it from the repository."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil gá leis an gcomhad aistriúcháin don teanga fhoinseach, bain den "
"stór é le do thoil."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:22
msgid ""
"If the translation file for the source language is needed, but should be "
"ignored by Weblate, please adjust the language filter to exclude it."
msgstr ""
"Más gá an comhad aistriúcháin don teanga fhoinseach, ach gur cheart do "
"Weblate neamhaird a dhéanamh air, le do thoil coigeartaigh an scagaire "
"teanga chun é a eisiamh."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:31
msgid ""
"The component contains several translation files mapped to a single language "
"in Weblate."
msgstr ""
"Tá roinnt comhad aistriúcháin sa chomhpháirt atá mapáilte go teanga amháin "
"in Weblate."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:32
msgid "Please fix this by removing one of the translation files."
msgstr "Déan é seo a dheisiú trí cheann de na comhaid aistriúcháin a bhaint."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:39
msgid ""
"Avoid having translation files for both the plain language code and its "
"equivalent territory designation (for example de and de_DE)."
msgstr ""
"Seachain comhaid aistriúcháin a bheith agat don chód gnáththeanga agus don "
"ainmniú críche coibhéiseach (mar shampla de agus de_DE)."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:52
msgid "Language codes"
msgstr "Cóid teanga"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatelanguage.html:53
msgid "File names"
msgstr "Ainmneacha comhaid"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:3
msgid "The component contains several duplicated translation strings."
msgstr "Tá roinnt teaghráin aistriúcháin dhúbailt sa chomhpháirt."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:12
#: weblate/templates/translate.html:420 weblate/templates/translate.html:523
msgid "Source"
msgstr "Foinse"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/duplicatestring.html:33
msgid ""
"Please fix this by removing duplicated strings with same identifier from the "
"translation files."
msgstr ""
"Déan é seo a shocrú le do thoil trí teaghráin dhúblacha a bhfuil an t-"
"aitheantóir céanna orthu a bhaint de na comhaid aistriúcháin."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/extractpotmissingmsgmerge.html:3
msgid ""
"This component updates the POT file automatically, but does not update the "
"PO files."
msgstr ""
"Nuashonraíonn an chomhpháirt seo an comhad POT go huathoibríoch, ach ní "
"nuashonraíonn sé na comhaid PO."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/extractpotmissingmsgmerge.html:6
msgid ""
"Install the msgmerge add-on as well if you want translation files to follow "
"template changes automatically."
msgstr ""
"Suiteáil an breiseán msgmerge chomh maith más mian leat go leanfaidh comhaid "
"aistriúcháin athruithe teimpléid go huathoibríoch."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:4
msgid ""
"The last webhook update for this component used fallback repository matching "
"instead of an exact repository URL match."
msgstr ""
"Bhain an nuashonrú webhook deireanach don chomhpháirt seo úsáid as "
"meaitseáil stóir chúltaca in ionad meaitseáil URL stóir cruinn."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:8
msgid ""
"This can happen when the component repository URL does not match the "
"repository URL sent by the webhook, or when Weblate does not yet understand "
"the repository URL format in the webhook payload."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis seo tarlú nuair nach mbíonn URL stórais an chomhpháirte ag "
"teacht leis an URL stórais a sheol an webhook, nó nuair nach dtuigeann "
"Weblate formáid URL an stórais san ualach webhook fós."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:12
msgid ""
"Check the component repository URL first. If the URL is correct, report the "
"issue to Weblate with the webhook service name, configured component "
"repository URL, branch, and repository URLs from the webhook payload."
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil URL stórtha an chomhpháirte ar dtús. Más ceart an URL, cuir an "
"fhadhb in iúl do Weblate leis an ainm seirbhíse webhook, URL stórtha an "
"chomhpháirte cumraithe, an brainse, agus URLanna stórtha ón ualach webhook."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:16
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Inexact webhook matching is currently scheduled for removal in Weblate "
"2026.9, see <a href=\"%(issue_url)s\">issue #19855</a>."
msgstr ""
"Tá sé sceidealaithe faoi láthair go mbainfear meaitseáil neamhchruinn ar an "
"webhook i Weblate 2026.9, féach <a href=\"%(issue_url)s\">eisiúint #19855</"
"a>."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:24
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Seirbhís"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:30
msgid "Repository URL"
msgstr "URL an Stórais"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:36
msgid "Repository name"
msgstr "Ainm an stórais"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:42
msgid "Branch"
msgstr "Brainse"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:52
msgid "Configure component"
msgstr "Cumraigh an chomhpháirt"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexacthookmatch.html:58
msgid "Report issue"
msgstr "Eisiúint tuairisce"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:3
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unsupportedconfiguration.html:3
#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/unusedenforcedcheck.html:3
msgid "This component is set up incorrectly."
msgstr "Tá an chomhpháirt seo socraithe go mícheart."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:5
msgid "Following files are no longer present in the repository:"
msgstr "Níl na comhaid seo a leanas i láthair sa stór a thuilleadh:"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/inexistantfiles.html:16
#: weblate/trans/models/component.py:678
msgid "Template for new translations"
msgstr "Teimpléad le haghaidh aistriúcháin nua"

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/mergefailure.html:3
msgid "Weblate could not merge upstream changes while updating the repository."
msgstr ""
"Níorbh fhéidir le Weblate athruithe réamhtheachtacha a chumasc agus an stór "
"á nuashonrú."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/missinglicense.html:4
msgid ""
"Any publicly available project should have defined license to indicate what "
"terms apply to contributions."
msgstr ""
"Ba cheart go mbeadh ceadúnas sainithe ag aon tionscadal atá ar fáil go "
"poiblí chun a léiriú cad iad na téarmaí a bhaineann le ranníocaíochtaí."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualglossary.html:4
msgid ""
"Using monolingual files as a glossary is not recommended because adding "
"strings to target language only is not possible in monolingual files."
msgstr ""
"Ní mholtar comhaid aonteangacha a úsáid mar ghluais mar ní féidir teaghráin "
"a chur leis an sprioctheanga amháin i gcomhaid aonteangacha."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualglossary.html:7
msgid ""
"You can continue using the glossary this way, but some features will be "
"unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat leanúint leis an ngluais a úsáid ar an mbealach seo, ach ní "
"bheidh roinnt gnéithe ar fáil."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualtranslation.html:3
msgid ""
"The translation component looks monolingual, but it is not set up to be."
msgstr ""
"Tá cuma aonteangach ar chomhpháirt an aistriúcháin, ach níl sé socraithe le "
"bheith."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/monolingualtranslation.html:4
msgid "Please add a monolingual base language file in the component settings."
msgstr "Cuir comhad bonnteanga aonteangach leis sna socruithe comhpháirteanna."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nolibreconditions.html:3
msgid "This project does no longer fit into Libre hosting conditions."
msgstr ""
"Ní luíonn an tionscadal seo le coinníollacha óstála Libre a thuilleadh."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:3
msgid "No translations were found for this component file mask."
msgstr "Ní bhfuarthas aon aistriúcháin don masc comhaid comhpháirte seo."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:6
msgid "This is okay when the repository does not contain translations yet."
msgstr "Tá sé seo ceart go leor nuair nach bhfuil aistriúcháin sa stór fós."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:8
msgid ""
"The alert will disappear once translations are added in Weblate or committed "
"to the repository."
msgstr ""
"Imeoidh an foláireamh as radharc a luaithe a chuirfear aistriúcháin leis i "
"Weblate nó a chuirfear sa stór iad."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:12
msgid ""
"Starting new translations directly in Weblate is possible, and creates files "
"based on the file mask."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir tús a chur le haistriúcháin nua go díreach in Weblate, agus "
"cruthaítear comhaid bunaithe ar an masc comhaid."

#: weblate/templates/trans/alert/nomaskmatches.html:16
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If translations already exist, check whether the file mask "
"<code>%(filemask)s</code> matches files in your version control system "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"Más ann d’aistriúcháin cheana féin, seiceáil an bhfuil an masc comhaid "
"<code>%(filemask)s</code> ag teacht le comhaid i stórlann do chórais "
"rialaithe leaganacha."

